Package: rdataviz
Title: World-Class Data Visualization Themes and Utilities for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("AI", "Developer", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Contributors", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for creating publication-quality, accessible
    data visualizations in R. Provides ggplot2 themes with dark/light mode support,
    colorblind-safe palettes following WCAG guidelines, plotly theming utilities,
    and reusable chart templates. Designed for both static reports and interactive
    Shiny dashboards with a focus on data communication excellence.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/user/rdataviz
BugReports: https://github.com/user/rdataviz/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
